"title": "6239: prostitution",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6239",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture condemns the offering of sex for money or favours. However, it also stresses the prospect of new life in Christ for prostitutes, and points to some prostitutes as examples of faith.</p>\n<h2>Prostitution among the heathen</h2>\n<h3>For money</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:15-Gen38:16\">GEN 38:15–38:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:1\">JOS 2:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:3\">JOL 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Religious prostitution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:21-Gen38:22\">GEN 38:21–38:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:14\">JOB 36:14</a></p>\n<h2>Prostitution in Israel</h2>\n<h3>It was forbidden under God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:29\">LEV 19:29</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:17-Deut23:18\">DEU 23:17–23:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Priests were forbidden to marry prostitutes</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:7\">LEV 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:14\">LEV 21:14</a></p>\n<h3>The penalties for prostitution</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:24\">GEN 38:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:9\">LEV 21:9</a></p>\n<h3>Efforts to remove the shrine-prostitutes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11-1Kgs15:12\">1KI 15:11–15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:45-1Kgs22:46\">1KI 22:45–22:46</a></p>\n<h3>The lure of prostitution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:10\">PRO 7:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9\">1CO 6:9</a></p>\n<h3>The prevalaence of prostitution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:24\">1KI 14:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:16\">1KI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:7\">JER 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:13-Hos4:14\">HOS 4:13–4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:10\">HOS 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:7\">MIC 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against prostitution</h2>\n<h3>It has dire consequences</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:25-Prov6:27\">PRO 6:25–6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:1-Judg16:2\">JDG 16:1–16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:26-Prov23:27\">PRO 23:26–23:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:3\">PRO 29:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:30\">LUK 15:30</a></p>\n<h3>Christians must avoid it</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:15-1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:15–6:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Prostitutes can be redeemed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:31-Matt21:32\">MAT 21:31–21:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:37-Luke7:50\">LUK 7:37–7:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:31\">HEB 11:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:25\">JAS 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:22-Josh6:25\">JOS 6:22–6:25</a></p>\n<h2>Prostitution as a metaphor</h2>\n<h3>For worldly corruption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:1-Rev17:5\">REV 17:1–17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:15-Isa23:17\">ISA 23:15–23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:4\">NAM 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>For apostasy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:16\">DEU 31:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:15-Exod34:16\">EXO 34:15–34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:5\">LEV 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:17\">JDG 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:27\">JDG 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:33\">JDG 8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:25\">1CH 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:39\">PSA 106:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:21\">ISA 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:16-Ezek16:17\">EZK 16:16–16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:26\">EZK 16:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:28\">EZK 16:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:33-Ezek16:34\">EZK 16:33–16:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:41\">EZK 16:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:1-Ezek23:35\">EZK 23:1–23:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:10-Hos4:12\">HOS 4:10–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:4\">HOS 5:4</a></p>",
